/* create a program that will ask the users name, age, and reddit 
username. have it tell them the information back, in the format:

your name is (blank), you are (blank) years old, and your username 
is (blank) 

for extra credit, have the program log this information
in a file to be accessed later. */

name = prompt("Please tell me your name:");
age = prompt("Please tell me your age");
username = prompt("Please tell me your username");

console.log("Your name is " + name + ", your age is " + age + 
", your username is " + username + ".");
